void llvm::SmallPtrSetIteratorImpl::AdvanceIfNotValid ( )
inlineprotected

AdvanceIfNotValid - If the current bucket isn't valid, advance to a bucket that is. This is guaranteed to stop because the end() bucket is marked valid.
